  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This is an open parallel design randomized trial of amiodarone plus a beta blocker vs a beta
      blocker alone vs sotalol for the prevention of ICD shocks in patients receiving an ICD for
      spontaneous or inducible ventricular tachycardia or fibrillation
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
